---
title: Tempura Fried Cheese over Rice & Mixed Greens with Creamy Lemon Sauce
description: Don’t let its name fool you—grilling cheese is great on the grill, but it’s also fantastic fried! Here you’ll coat it in a garlicky tempura batter, then fry in a hot pan until crispy on the outside and magically melty on the inside. Once golden, the cheese is served over jasmine rice and mixed greens, then topped with a drizzle of creamy lemon sauce and a sprinkle of toasted sunflower seeds. Yep, this meal is guaranteed to serve up smiles. Say (fried) cheese!
